火箭弹，没有人员伤亡报告 ■ 以色列国防军称袭击了真主党防空系统</description><pubDate>Sat, 29 Jun 2024 03:02:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article-live/irans-mission-to-un-if-israel-attacks-lebanon-an-obliterating-war-will-ensue/00000190-61e4-d90c-a7fc-77e4c4ba0000</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构报告称，伊朗计划在福尔多安装一半新离心机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/iran-installs-half-of-planned-new-centrifuges-at-fordow-iaea-report-says/00000190-60bf-d499-a5bf-e9bfc5930000</link><description>外交官表示，增加IR-6机器是对国际原子能机构35国理事会6月5日针对伊朗的一项决议的回应，该决议呼吁德黑兰加强与监督机构的合作，并撤销最近禁止检查人员的做法</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 21:38:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/iran-installs-half-of-planned-new-centrifuges-at-fordow-iaea-report-says/00000190-60bf-d499-a5bf-e9bfc5930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：三架来自黎巴嫩的无人机在加利利西部爆炸，25枚火箭弹向北部发射</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-three-drones-from-lebanon-explode-in-western-galilee-25-rockets-fired-at-north/00000190-609d-d009-a9f8-6a9fdf010000</link><description>由于拦截尝试失败，真主党的火箭弹和无人机袭击导致以色列北部两匹马死亡，一辆面包车着火。北方议会主席表示：“纳斯鲁拉一次证明了他是主权者”</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 21:27:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-29/ty-article/.premium/idf-three-drones-from-lebanon-explode-in-western-galilee-25-rockets-fired-at-north/00000190-609d-d009-a9f8-6a9fdf010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部国防部长加兰特：“我们并不是在寻求战争，但我们已经做好了准备”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/defense-minister-gallant-in-northern-israel-not-looking-for-war-but-ready-for-one/00000190-6062-d499-a5bf-e9fef9b80000</link><description>格兰特告诉士兵，“我们正在准备我们的防御和进攻能力”，并“研究战争的外交替代方案” ■ 美国攻击舰部署在地中海东部作为“威慑”</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 20:38:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/defense-minister-gallant-in-northern-israel-not-looking-for-war-but-ready-for-one/00000190-6062-d499-a5bf-e9fef9b80000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列，第 266 天：以色列国防部长表示，以色列并不希望北方发生战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-266-israel-isnt-the-one-who-wants-war-in-north-defense-minister-says/00000190-5fa5-d90c-a7fc-7fa5bad50000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，它在加沙市舒贾亚附近开展了“地上和地下”行动 ■ 以色列高等法院命令该州在一个月内做出回应，请愿书要求成立国家委员会调查 10 月 7 日的事件 ■ 美国转移军事资产距离以色列和黎巴嫩更近，以防需要撤离美国人 ■ 这是战争开始 266 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 16:53:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-266-israel-isnt-the-one-who-wants-war-in-north-defense-minister-says/00000190-5fa5-d90c-a7fc-7fa5bad50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙南部的战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-fighting-in-southern-gaza/00000190-5e1a-d63a-a7b2-5f1f2ee80000</link><description>埃亚尔·希尼斯中士，19 岁，来自阿菲克基布兹，曾在纳哈尔旅服役。他的基布兹形容他很安静，随时准备提供帮助，并说他喜欢足球和动物</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 14:27:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-fighting-in-southern-gaza/00000190-5e1a-d63a-a7b2-5f1f2ee80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队表示，一名巴勒斯坦人在对杰宁的袭击中丧生。他的家人却不这么认为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-06-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-army-said-a-palestinian-was-killed-in-a-raid-his-family-believes-otherwise/00000190-5ee8-d506-ab9a-7eea278c0000</link><description>维萨姆·哈农是如军方所说，7个月前被以色列国防军杀害，还是如他父母所说，他是很久之后被拍到躺在哈达萨医院昏迷不醒的人？以色列不归还尸体的习惯让家庭在绝望与希望之间左右为难</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 13:21:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-06-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-israeli-army-said-a-palestinian-was-killed-in-a-raid-his-family-believes-otherwise/00000190-5ee8-d506-ab9a-7eea278c0000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列人几乎没有任何真正的共同点”：埃特加·凯雷特的采访</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israelis-hardly-have-any-true-common-denominator-an-interview-with-etgar-keret/00000190-5e82-d0b3-a7d1-7fce202d0000</link><description>对于以色列作家埃特加·凯雷特来说，即使事情分崩离析，写作仍然可以成为对话的基础。只是不要让他在反政府示威中发言</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 12:52:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israelis-hardly-have-any-true-common-denominator-an-interview-with-etgar-keret/00000190-5e82-d0b3-a7d1-7fce202d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列法院命令警方将缴获的模型坦克归还给抗议团体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-orders-police-to-return-model-tank-to-protest-group-after-seizing-it/00000190-5e59-d63a-a7b2-5f5f2fae0000</link><description>哈德拉治安法院法官驳回了警方的说法，即泡沫罐在凯撒利亚的反政府抗议活动中出现后，在公众中“传播了恐惧”。该模型坦克属于“Kippur 73战斗机”抗议团体</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 11:59:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/israeli-court-orders-police-to-return-model-tank-to-protest-group-after-seizing-it/00000190-5e59-d63a-a7b2-5f5f2fae0000</guid></item><item><title>还不要歌颂耶路撒冷：哪些人口统计数据无法告诉您这座城市的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/dont-eulogize-jerusalem-yet-what-demographics-dont-tell-you-about-the-citys-future/00000190-5e26-d90c-a7fc-7f26a4a70000</link><description>由于其人口状况，人们常常预测耶路撒冷的未来会很黯淡。但真实的情况要乐观得多</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 11:00:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/dont-eulogize-jerusalem-yet-what-demographics-dont-tell-you-about-the-citys-future/00000190-5e26-d90c-a7fc-7f26a4a70000</guid></item><item><title>“严重损害治理”：极右翼MK寻求改变以色列司法监察员的任命程序</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mk-seeks-to-change-appointment-process-of-israels-judiciary-ombudsman/00000190-5de7-d90c-a7fc-7fe75fc90000</link><description>罗斯曼表示，该法案旨在阻止法官选择负责调查他们的监察员。法院法律顾问声称，监察员的政治任命可能会导致法官被政治罢免</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 09:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mk-seeks-to-change-appointment-process-of-israels-judiciary-ombudsman/00000190-5de7-d90c-a7fc-7fe75fc90000</guid></item><item><title>斯莫特里奇因担心巴勒斯坦权力机构崩溃而取消冻结巴勒斯坦权力机构税收资金的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-to-cancel-decision-to-freeze-palestinian-authority-tax-funds-fearing-collapse/00000190-5dab-de5e-abd0-fffb6de10000</link><description>财政部长决定转移以色列代表巴勒斯坦权力机构征收的税收资金，上个月表示他将冻结这些资金“直至另行通知”。预计他还将宣布西岸的五个非法前哨基地合法化</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 08:19:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-to-cancel-decision-to-freeze-palestinian-authority-tax-funds-fearing-collapse/00000190-5dab-de5e-abd0-fffb6de10000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡不再控制以色列的事态发展——这让他心烦意乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-no-longer-controls-events-in-israel-and-its-driving-him-to-distraction/00000190-5b17-def3-a5b6-db37f5d80000</link><description>以色列最高法院关于正统征兵豁免的裁决可能会产生改变现实的影响 ■ 如果还有人有任何疑问，本周情况变得更加明确：内塔尼亚胡不会同意就 10 月 7 日的灾难成立调查委员会 ■ 以色列是否已经通过了“法国法”，尽管议会还没有通过它？ ■ 击败哈马斯与司法“改革”的区别</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 03:03:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-no-longer-controls-events-in-israel-and-its-driving-him-to-distraction/00000190-5b17-def3-a5b6-db37f5d80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡正在发动三场消耗战：针对哈马斯、真主党和以色列人民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-three-wars-of-attrition-against-hamas-hezbollah-and-the-israeli-people/00000190-5af8-d1c4-affa-5bfee2a50000</link><description>以色列总理希望他的人民继续处于不确定性的迷雾中，使他们更加依赖功能失调的政府 ■ 与真主党爆发全面战争的可能性似乎比几天前要小 — — 但这并不意味着敌对行动已经结束 ■ 以色列国防军正在适应新的战斗强度不断变化的惯例</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 03:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-three-wars-of-attrition-against-hamas-hezbollah-and-the-israeli-people/00000190-5af8-d1c4-affa-5bfee2a50000</guid></item><item><title>“当人们听说我要去以色列时，他们会感到不安”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-28/ty-article/.highlight/when-people-hear-that-im-going-to-israel-they-get-upset/00000190-5c98-d7e5-a1f3-dd990d5b0000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一位美国犹太人前往以色列三天，第一次见到她的团队成员，两位七十多岁的姐妹回忆起她们在爱情方面做出的选择</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 02:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-06-28/ty-article/.highlight/when-people-hear-that-im-going-to-israel-they-get-upset/00000190-5c98-d7e5-a1f3-dd990d5b0000</guid></item><item><title>官员称，由于天气原因，美国将拆除加沙援助码头，并且可能不会将其恢复原状</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article-live/smotrich-backtracks-on-decision-to-withhold-funds-from-pa-fearing-its-collapse/00000190-5c9f-d7e5-a1f3-dd9ff3360000</link><description>以色列军方表示，从黎巴嫩南部发射了三架无人机和 25 枚火箭，没有人员伤亡报告 ■ 以色列国防军称袭击了真主党防空系统 ■ 美国将攻击舰转移到地中海，以阻止以色列与黎巴嫩冲突升级的风险 ■ 以色列国防军在加沙发起基于情报的行动城市的 Shujaiya 社区；加沙人报告 30 人死亡 ■ 斯莫特里奇收回向巴勒斯坦权力机构扣留资金的决定 ■ 美国敦促公民“强烈重新考虑”黎巴嫩旅行</description><pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 02:23:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-28/ty-article-live/smotrich-backtracks-on-decision-to-withhold-funds-from-pa-fearing-its-collapse/00000190-5c9f-d7e5-a1f3-dd9ff3360000</guid></item><item><title>拜登：“我们拯救了以色列”；特朗普：“他变得像巴勒斯坦人”：第一场总统辩论中的灾难性表现与不断的谎言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-06-28/ty-article/.premium/biden-trump-clash-over-israel-iran-and-anti